title: U.S. has breached trade deal and Europe is ready to retaliate, top trade lawmaker tells CNBC
summary_full: The U.S. has breached the terms of its trade deal with the European Union "several times," top EU trade lawmaker Bernd Lange told CNBC.
summary_public: The U.S. has breached the terms of its trade deal with the European Union "several times," top EU trade lawmaker Bernd Lange told CNBC.
